# House Price Prediction using Machine Learning 🏠📈

## 📌 Overview
This project predicts house prices using machine learning algorithms based on various real estate features.

## 🎯 Problem Statement
House prices depend on multiple factors such as location, size, and number of rooms. Manual estimation is inaccurate and inconsistent.

## 🛠️ Tech Stack
- Python
- Pandas, NumPy
- Scikit-learn
- Jupyter Notebook

## ✨ Features
- Data cleaning & preprocessing
- Exploratory Data Analysis (EDA)
- Feature engineering
- ML model training and evaluation

## ⚙️ Workflow
1. Data preprocessing
2. Feature selection
3. Model training
4. Performance evaluation

